short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: T-Bot RPA浏览器自动化插件

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Send a message to a native application for T-Bot RPA to automate the page.This extension allows you to interact with the T-Bot RPA local application, enabling the automation of various web page tasks. By sending messages to T-Bot RPA, you can initiate, control, and monitor automated processes, thereby improving efficiency and saving time. Whether it's filling out forms, clicking buttons, or other actions, this extension can help you automatically complete various web page tasks. Please note that using this extension requires the prior installation and configuration of the T-Bot RPA local application.
